{"tid":2402906,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警屍境界｜王喜專欄","createTime":"2021-02-10T17:44:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T17:44:58.000Z","uid":261647,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a27e497d3efffd0375cf5fcc9843e0822ca8bfd8","tid":2402906,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T17:44:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/gelekchodar/posts/3621598451289893\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgelekchodar%2Fposts%2F3621598451289893&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhbV8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=96ea97df\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/gelekchodar/posts/3621598451289893</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：WONG HE 王喜<br />\n<br />\n喜出望外 之 警屍境界<br />\n<br />\n善男子啊 你是不是很想知道，報案人為什麼打999報警救助，口述一次現場情況，經接線生通知消防救護及轉交該警區的電台接手處理，而不按內線直接通知行兩步就到現場的灣仔警署報案室值日官呢？難道這位報案人重案組督察朝九晚五的警務生涯中，初次目睹死屍，露出屋邨少婦心，忘掉黃竹坑那廿九幾週「嚴格專業」、「臨危不亂」、「無畏無懼」的警察訓練？不過，事實證明，報案人目測判死的功夫，相當精準，因為，消防救護到場給你施行約十分鐘急救後，於同日0915時，證實你已死亡；你也覺得奇怪，對嗎？為何不邊做CPR，邊由警車開路護送就近醫院，由急診室醫生負起做certify的責任呢？（全文刊於<a href=\"https://s.nextmag.hk/e/7enzTMovJdb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmag.hk%2Fe%2F7enzTMovJdb&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhbV8WQSydv6El4C3YWjT4Eg%3D&h=c1b75a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmag.hk/e/7enzTMovJdb</a>）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dnNiqUc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdnNiqUc.png&h=c4a6eb8e&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}